name: Soshu_Londahl
content:
Soshu Londahl was an Ithorian author. Londahl wrote "Life's Memories," which was published in his anthology Lyrical Metaphysics: Ode on an Odon by Coruscani Publishing. It was later quoted by San Herrera and Nia Reston in their paper also named "Life's Memories."
Soshu Londahl was mentioned in Life Memories, an article published in 2003 as a tie-in to the Living Force adventure Excursion.
